Title: A Note on Dual Superconductivity and Confinement

Authors: W. Garcia Fuertes (Universidad de Oviedo) and J. Mateos Guilarte

(Universidad de Salamanca)Comments: 9 pages, no figures. Accepted for publication in Physics Letters B

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B437 (1998) 82-87

Electric self-dual vortices arising as BPS states in the strong couplinglimit of N=2 supersymmetric Yang-Mills theory, softly broken to N=1, arereported.